      </a>
      <a class="post-card" href="/blog/human-in-the-loop-ai-approval-gates/">
        <h4>Human-in-the-Loop by Design</h4>
        <p>Approval gates that prevent expensive AI mistakes.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="post-card" href="/blog/openclaw-march-2026-reliability-updates/">
        <h4>OpenClaw March 2026 Reliability Updates</h4>
        <p>The update changes that improve real-world agent reliability.</p>
